<a class="btn btn-primary" href="?sortby=shifts">Shifts</a>
<a class="btn btn-primary" href="?sortby=eot"><img src="~/images/egg_truth.png" /></a>
<a class="btn btn-primary" href="?sortby=eott"><img src="~/images/egg_truth.png" alt="Eggs of Truth" /> w/Unclaimed</a>
<a class="btn btn-primary" href="?sortby=eov">Total Eggs Of Virtue</a>
<a class="btn btn-primary" href="?sortby=tepershift">TE/Shift</a>



